&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;#LI-Hybrid&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bosa Properties is looking for a Senior Marketing Manager to join our team of talented marketing professionals. Reporting to the Senior Director, Marketing, this role leads cross-functional go-to-market planning and oversees execution across multiple initiatives. You translate strategic direction into clear, actionable marketing plans, aligning teams, channels, and resources to deliver measurable business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for a senior marketer who thrives at the intersection of strategy, planning rigor, and execution, and who leads through influence, clarity, and strong cross-functional relation&lt;strong&gt;ships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Plan Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional marketing planning in partnership with the Senior Director, translating strategic priorities into integrated go-to-market plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct tactical planning and execution across sales, brand, growth, creative, and insights teams through influence rather than authority.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Distill complex business requirements into clear marketing blueprints, including objectives, target audiences, timelines, KPIs, and success measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop project-level marketing plans encompassing channel mix, messaging frameworks, content calendars, activation tactics, and detailed timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional &amp;amp; Execution Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate cross-team alignment to ensure shared priorities, sequencing, and readiness for execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and orchestrate execution across multiple initiatives, maintaining momentum and accountability across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide day-to-day oversight of campaign execution, ensuring work is delivered on strategy, on time, and on budget.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own briefing for key initiatives, ensuring clarity, consistency, and alignment with brand positioning and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insights, Optimization &amp;amp; Performance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze historical performance, market insights, and business data to evaluate plans and inform decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish performance expectations and continuously optimize plans based on results, learnings, and changing market conditions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the customer by developing a deep understanding of the business and customer journey through strong internal partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;

