&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;#LI-Hybrid&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the EVP, Revenue &amp;amp; Growth, you will own the intelligence and technology agenda across the business - the data and AI capability, the technology team, and the transformation work that connects both to how the business actually operates. You will be a genuine peer at the senior leadership table, not a supporting function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The strongest candidates will be fluent in technology without having spent their entire careers inside it - systems thinkers who recognise patterns across cycles and contexts, and who have the operational discipline to turn that recognition into delivery.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the data and intelligence capability that moves decision-making from instinct to insight, and govern the enterprise AI strategy as a deliberate capability - not a feature.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a capable technology team and create the conditions for it to operate as a genuine business partner - with a commercial lens on what to build, buy, or retire.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive transformation across the business’s value chain - shaping the agenda, translating strategy into financially viable plans, and holding delivery across functions as a peer to the senior team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep fluency in data, data architecture, and analytics - the Intelligence Layer is the heart of this mandate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A history at the intersection of technology and business performance in an asset-intensive or operationally complex environment - shaping decisions, not managing a backlog.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The pattern recognition, stakeholder fluency, and comfort with ambiguity to earn trust across organisational boundaries and shape a mandate that will keep evolving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Total compensation includes a competitive base salary, performance bonus, and comprehensive benefits.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
